\begin{problem}{4.3.N (10)}
For  $n > 1$, let  $S_n = \sum_{k=2}^n \frac{1}{(k-1)k(k+1)}$. Find and prove by induction a formula that expresses $S_n$ in terms of $n$.
\end{problem}
